Perimeter Defense - Email Security > [T2]: Secure Email Attachments: Multi Antivirus Engines

Multi Antivirus Engines

 

Figure - zoom in

Most email security gateways include one or two AV engines to scan attachments for malicious content. Whenever possible, use an AV engine on the mail gateway different from the one deployed on endpoints. For example, if your enterprise AV solution is Sophos, use the MacAfee AV engine on the email gateway. This way, if one engine fails to detect the threat, the other may catch it.
